      <title>欧洲央行将利率维持在历史高位，暗示即将降息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-holds-rates-record-highs-signals-upcoming-cut-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行周四将利率维持在历史高位，但发出了更明确的信号，即随着欧元区通胀持续下降，欧洲央行可能准备降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-holds-rates-record-highs-signals-upcoming-cut-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 12:18:29 GMT</pubDate>
